headline: Omnicom (OMC) Q1 Earnings Preview: What You Should Know Beyond the Headline Estimates
summary: Besides Wall Street's top -and-bottom-line estimates for Omnicom (OMC), review projections for some of its key metrics to gain a deeper understanding of how the company might have fared during the quarter ended March 2025.
